     :arg x: Buffer to borrow
     :type x: `c_ptr(uint(8))` or `c_ptr(int(8))`

     :arg length: Length of the buffer `x`, excluding the terminating null byte.

     :arg size: Size of memory allocated for `x` in bytes

     :returns: A new :type:`bytes`
